OL,3,CGrandmother gets $3.8 million after
OL,4,CiPhone error sends SWAT team to her
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FA grandmother in Denver in the United
OL,8,FStates has won a $3.76 million (#3
OL,9,Fmillion) jury verdict after her home
OL,10,Fwas wrongfully searched by a SWAT team
OL,11,Fthanks to an iPhone app.
OL,13,FA team of armed officers attended Ruby
OL,14,FJohnson's property searching for a
OL,15,Fstolen truck, which contained guns and
OL,16,Fto the 78-year-old's home using the
OL,17,FFind My app.
