OL,7,FThe lawsuit alleged that police got a
OL,8,Fsearch warrant based on the
OL,9,Finformation as they attempted to find
OL,10,Fthe stolen vehicle, which contained
OL,11,Ffour semi-automatic handguns, a rifle,
OL,12,Fa revolver, two drones, $4,000
OL,13,F(#3,140) cash and .
OL,15,FA jury ruled in Ms Johnson's favour
OL,16,Funder a new Colorado law which allows
OL,17,Fpeople to sue the police over
OL,18,Fviolations of their state.
