OL,7,FDetective Gary Staab had wrongly
OL,8,Fobtained the warrant to search the
OL,9,Fseptuagenarian's home because he did
OL,10,Fnot point out that the app's
OL,11,Finformation is not precise and
OL,12,Fprovides only a general location of
OL,13,Fwhere a phone could be, the lawsuit
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe iPhone tracking data was given to
OL,17,Fpolice by the man who owned the stolen
OL,18,Ftruck and its contents.
