OL,3,CGrandmother gets $3.8 million after
OL,4,CiPhone error sends SWAT team to her
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FIt said Ms Johnson, a retired postal
OL,8,Fservice worker, had just got out of
OL,9,Fthe shower on January 4, 2022 when she
OL,10,Fheard a loud announcement for anybody
OL,11,Fin the house to exit the building with
OL,12,Ftheir hands up.
OL,14,FWearing only a bathrobe, she opened
OL,15,Fher front door to see an armoured
OL,16,Fvehicle on her doorstep, police
OL,17,Fvehicles lining the street, and men in
OL,18,Ffull military uniform carrying rifles
OL,19,Fwith a police dog.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/8
