OL,3,CGrandmother gets $3.8 million after
OL,4,CiPhone error sends SWAT team to her
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FThe police used a battering ram to get
OL,8,Finto Ms Johnson's garage even though
OL,9,Fshe had explained how to open the door.
OL,11,FThey broke the ceiling tiles to get
OL,12,Finto her attic, standing on top of one
OL,13,Fof her brand new dining room chairs,
OL,14,Faccording to the lawsuit.
OL,16,FOfficials also broke the head off a
OL,17,Fdoll created to look just like her,
OL,18,Fcomplete with glasses, American Civil
OL,19,FLiberties Union (ACLU) of Colorado
OL,20,Flegal director Tim Macdonald said.
