OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FIt is unclear whether the truck and
OL,8,Fits contents were found and returned
OL,9,Fto the owner.
OL,11,FMr Macdonald said the biggest damage
OL,12,Fwas done to Ms Johnson's sense of
OL,13,Fsafety in the home where she raised
OL,14,Fthree children as a single mother.
OL,16,FShe suffered ulcers and had trouble
OL,17,Fsleeping, before she eventually moved
OL,18,Fto a different neighbourhood.
