OL,7,F"For us, the damage was always about
OL,8,Fthe psychological and the emotional
OL,9,Fharm to Ms Johnson," he said.
OL,11,FThe lawsuit was brought under a
OL,12,Fprovision of a sweeping police reform
OL,13,Fbill passed in 2020 and is the first
OL,14,Fsignificant case to go to trial, the
OL,15,FACLU of Colorado said.
OL,17,FState lawmakers created a right to sue
OL,18,Findividual police officers for state
OL,19,Fconstitutional violations in state
OL,20,Fcourt.
